Package: segprof
Title: Customer Segment Profiler with Automatic Segmentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jajat", "L.", email = "jajatlesmana3@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jajat L.", role = "cph", comment = "Copyright holder")
  )
Description: Provides a function seg_prof() that automatically segments 
    customers using RFM and K-means (or uses existing segments) and 
    generates professional summary tables and visualizations 
    (bar chart, radar, 2D scatter with ellipses, 3D scatter). 
    Handles mixed data types (numeric, categorical) robustly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jajat/segprof
BugReports: https://github.com/jajat/segprof/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
